description:
ProfileSpotifies

Allows you to embed spotify songs, artists, playlists, etc into your profile and allow anyone with this plugin to see them.

- To use you need to find the id of each item you want. The easiesy way to do this is to copy the link to the song.
- You can then take those ids and format them like so `spotify: track/5gFfE8UgFslvqjVQw7dktZ, track/085ngJ2SLzSY23HUljUptc:`
- Make sure to include the type(which should be included in the url you copied)
- Paste this somewhere in your bio

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Futuremappermydud/Emnity-ProfileSpotifies/main/dist/ProfileSpotifies.js
Source: https://github.com/Futuremappermydud/Emnity-ProfileSpotifies
